records.name: Wings By Hawks - Free Room Upgrade,30 Mints Spa, Guided Snorkeling Tour

location.address: Wings By Hawks Hotels Address: 11468 Bogan Villa Magu1 Goalhi, Kamadhoo 06020

descriptions.hotel: Make yourself at home in one of the 16 guestrooms, featuring kitchens. Rooms have private balconies. Complimentary wireless internet access is available to keep you connected. Conveniences include desks and separate sitting areas, and housekeeping is provided on request.
descriptions.direction: With a stay at Wings by Hawks Hotels in Kamadhoo, you'll be near the beach, and 10.8 mi (17.3 km) from Dharavandhoo Mosque. This guesthouse is within the region of Kihaadhuffaru Island Beach and Kihaadhuffaru Island Pier.
descriptions.general: Location We love guest houses for their home comfort and discreet service. Guest house «Wings by Hawks Hotels» is located in Baa Atoll. This guest house is located in 18 km from the city center.At the guest house Taste the local cuisine and have a rest in the restaurant. The following services are also available for the guests: a spa center. There are other services available for the guests of the guest house. For example, a laundry.
descriptions.other: Pamper yourself with onsite massages or enjoy recreation amenities such as an outdoor pool.
